<em class="cEmphasis">test_expr</em>
</div>    
</td>
    <td><a name="wp3714735"> </a><div class="pCellBodyLeft" >
&#160;
</div>    
</td>
    <td><a name="wp3714737"> </a><div class="pCellBodyLeft" >
Expression that should evaluate to TRUE for at least <em class="cEmphasis">min_cks</em> cycles and at most <em class="cEmphasis">max_cks</em> cycles after it is sampled TRUE.
</div>    
</td>
</tr>
</table>
