</div>    
</td>
    <td><a name="wp3714774"> </a><div class="pCellBodyLeft" >
The expression <em class="cEmphasis">test_expr</em> was held TRUE for exactly <em class="cEmphasis">min_cks</em> cycles (<em class="cEmphasis">min_cks</em> &gt; 0).
</div>    
</td>
</tr>
